    "course_title": "QUANTUM ELECTRONICS",
    "description": "Elementary aspects of Lagrange theory of fields and field quantization; Bose, Fermi and Pauli operators; interaction of fields; quantum theory of damping and fluctuations; applications to lasers, nonlinear optics, and quantum optics. Knowledge of lasers [such asPHYSICS/\u200bE\u00a0C\u00a0E\u00a0\u00a0546] and graduate-level electromagnetics [such asE\u00a0C\u00a0E\u00a0740orPHYSICS\u00a0721] strongly encouraged.",
